## Non-Theorems

```elixir
res = prove ~p"""
thf(q_type, type, q : $i>$i>$o).
thf(conj,conjecture,
  (?[X:$i]: ![Y: $i]: q @ X @ Y) | (?[U:$i]: ![V:$i]: ~ (q @ V @ U))
).
"""

format_result res
# Timeout
```

```elixir
res = prove ~p"""
thf(q_type, type, q: $i>$i>$o).
thf(conj,conjecture,
  ?[Y:$i]: ![X:$i]: ( (![Z:$i]: q @ X @ Z) | ~(q @ X @ Y) )
).
"""

format_result res
# Timeout
```

