## Example 7 (Congruence)

a) Congruence under endomorphisms

```elixir
res = prove ~p"""
thf(conj, conjecture,
  ![X:$i, Y:$i, F:$i>$i]: (
    (X = Y) => (F @ X = F @ Y)
  )
).
"""

format_result res
# THM
```

<!-- livebook:{"output_size":"full"} -->

```elixir
render res
```

```elixir
res = prove ~p"""
thf(leibniz_t, type, l: A > A > $o).
thf(leibniz_def, definition,
  l = ^[X, Y]: ![P]: P @ X => P @ Y
).
thf(conj, conjecture,
  ![X:$i, Y:$i, F:$i>$i]: (
    (l @ X @ Y) => (l @ (F @ X) @ (F @ Y))
